(62378, 106408, 0, 1, 'Nightlight', '', '2011-04-01 00:00:00', 2011, 30, 0, 6, 'Even when I know it''s not the first time I''ve been here \nMy heart would be leaping out my chest \nif you weren''t quite so near \nYou''re sorry you brought this mess around, \nyour conscience weighed you down \nGuilty dialogue, is all you''ve got now \n\nHow in all confusion am I buried in my tears? \nBrimming with the maddness of it where, \nwe watch as our tempers flare \nI''m sorry I hurt you when you were wrong, \nit doesn''t make me right \nYou can take it, you can have tonight \n\nBut if you leave the nightlight on \nI''ll be home when all has calmed \nI''ll miss you till dawn \nbut till then I''ll stay gone \n\nFurious and yet revenge has never been more fair \nThen I hear you locking me out as you \npretend that you don''t care \nof you and me no longer we, \nof love and life and how to be \nFrom now we''d take our different roads to get there \n\nBut if you leave the nightlight on \nI''ll be home when all has calmed \nI''ll miss you till dawn \nbut till then I''ll stay gone \n\nForget today and all the pieces of us \nI now refuse to claim as my own \nForget today and all the shadows of us \nI now deny the shortest way home \nForget today and all the moments we could not see past \ncoming out alone \nForget it all \n\nBut if you leave the nightlight on \nI''ll be home when all has calmed \nI''ll miss you till dawn \nbut till then I''ll stay gone', '', 217, '', '', '', '', 'Anie Fann 范安婷', '', 1, 0, 0, '2013-04-01 21:52:57', '2015-03-12 14:00:05', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
